        <tr><td>Multi-component repair</td><td>$700 to $1,400</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty</td><td>90 days parts and labor</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p class="price-note">$120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair. No emergency surcharge.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">06 · Brands we service</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Five deck oven platforms cover most LA pizzerias.</h2>

    <p><strong>Bakers Pride</strong> (Standex Food Service): Y-600 single deck, Y-602 double deck, Y-800 large. The dominant US deck oven. See <a href="/brands/bakers-pride-pizza-oven-repair/">Bakers Pride pizza oven repair</a>.</p>

    <p><strong>Marsal</strong> (independent, NY): MB-866 and MB-60 series. Premium NY-style pizzeria standard. Parts available through manufacturer distribution.</p>

    <p><strong>Cuppone</strong> (Italian independent): Tiziano electric deck. Naples-style premium, common in upscale Italian restaurants. Parts via Italian distribution, 5 to 10 day lead time.</p>

    <p><strong>Vulcan</strong> (ITW Food Equipment Group): less common deck configuration, but serviced.</p>

    <p><strong>Montague</strong> (Welbilt): heritage deck oven brand, parts available through Welbilt distribution.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">07 · Why operators call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Eight reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Multi-deck diagnostic.</strong> Bakers Pride Y-602 double-deck has independent thermostats per deck. We diagnose each deck separately.</li>
      <li><strong>Stone deck replacement capability.</strong> Year 12 to 15 thermal-cycling fatigue eventually cracks the deck. We replace with manufacturer-spec refractory.</li>
      <li><strong>Gas + electric expertise.</strong> Bakers Pride Y gas plus Cuppone Tiziano electric. Different repair scope, we handle both.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410.</strong> Verifiable.</li>
      <li><strong> scope.</strong></li>
      <li><strong>24/7 phone answering, no emergency surcharge.</strong> $120 anytime.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Pizzeria service-hour awareness.</strong> Lunch and dinner rush mean we schedule around prep time when possible.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/commercial/pizza-oven-repair/conveyor-pizza-oven-repair/">conveyor</a>, <a href="/commercial/pizza-oven-repair/wood-fired-pizza-oven-repair/">wood-fired</a>. Parent: <a href="/commercial/pizza-oven-repair/">commercial pizza oven repair</a>. Related: <a href="/commercial/oven-repair/">commercial oven repair</a>, <a href="/commercial/exhaust-hood-repair/">exhaust hood repair</a>. Credentials: <a href="/credentials/licensed/">BHGS license</a>, <a href="/credentials/epa-certified/">EPA 608</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
